data.description: Calling Builders, Developer's dream or design your own incredible new house in Hollywood Hills West/Sunset strip area, the prestigious Mount Olympus with view(from 2nd floor)! Remodel this fixer or built new 6,000 Sq Ft (plans and permits expired, can be renewed and transferred, if requested).  Home offers open floor plan, high ceiling, large  pool, deck/yard, patio, basement that may be converted to your needs of studio/maids/office. What a great opportunity, do not miss it!!!!  Pictures 9 to 18 are samples of properties in the same street or neighbors, all remodeled or rebuilt; some are in  construction..imagine to extend it to 6,000 sq ft, how amazing this house will be!!!!Do the comps and see :)
data.whatILove: A great fixer or extend to 6,000 Sq  Ft . Seller has plans and permits that can be renewed! View in the unique Mount Olympus, Hollywood Hills!
